0\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=420\u0026amp;h=420\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"420\" height=\"420\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Lexar 1TB Professional Go Portable SSD\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/untitled-design-9.png\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/untitled-design-9.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                                                                        \t\n\t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n    \t\t\t\t\t\tLexar 1TB Professional Go Portable SSD\n\t\t\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n                            \n                                                                                                                    \u003cp\u003e$130\n                                    \u003cspan\u003e$200\u003c/span\u003e\n                                    Save $70\n                                \u003c/p\u003e\n                                                    \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n                            \u003cp\u003eOne of the sleekest portable SSDs you can buy, making it a great way to add storage to your mobile devices. The best part is that it comes with a hub for creators, and is now available for just $130 for a limited time.\u003c/p\u003e\n            \n            \n            \n\n            \n            \n            \n                            \n            \n            \n            \n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt\u0026#39;s not easy to add storage to phones nowadays, as most \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-android-phones/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003etop-end devices\u003c/a\u003e don\u0026#39;t offer support for microSD cards. The good news is that \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-cloud-storage-options/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ecloud storage is a thing\u003c/a\u003e, and the USB-C port can also support a wide range of storage accessories as well. Now, it\u0026#39;s never going to be convenient to have something sticking out of your phone while you\u0026#39;re on the go, but if you have to, we think this Lexar SSD is going to be the best option. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/amazon-prime-day-2025-deals/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\u003cimg alt=\"Amazon Prime Day 2025 promotional banner from Android Police\" src=\"https://static0.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/img_0103.png\"/\u003e\n \u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNot only are you getting 1TB of storage in a sleek package, but this bundle also includes a hub, which will allow you to connect more accessories to your device as well, while also having an additional USB-C port for power. This is great if you\u0026#39;re doing something that requires the SSD to be constantly plugged in.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eThe best part is that this SSD is not just for phones, and can be used with a variety of other devices as well. So if you\u0026#39;ve been looking for an easy way to add storage to your devices, this Lexar SSD is going to be it. While it\u0026#39;s usually priced at $200, it can now be had at a pretty steep discount during \u003ca href=\"http://www.androidpolice.com/best-amazon-prime-day-2025-deals/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAmazon\u0026#39;s Prime Day sales event\u003c/a\u003e, which drops the price to just $130. This is the best discount we\u0026#39;ve seen for this device, so get it while you still can. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-lexar-professional-go-portable-ssd\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Lexar Professional Go Portable SSD?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n 